{"tid":2036913,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"趁咁夜，想同咁多位手足講樣嘢","createTime":"2020-05-26T17:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T18:22:42.000Z","uid":247494,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d6adc2caca13ebe2f5a1f3781cf6ac65f4528fa","tid":2036913,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"我相信有好多手足而家呢一刻係好緊張，諗緊送頭/唔送頭。<br />\n<br />\n不過我想你地諗下個目的：聽日行動為咗國際上make noise定還是唔想通過惡法？<br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴：除咗「利益」仲要當地人民頑強抵抗 先會令到國際出手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴講過每樣嘢靠自己奮鬥，唔好諗住做free rider<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一係唔做，一做就盡！</span><br />\n<br />\n我冇咩野同大家講，祝你地武運昌隆"},{"pid":"bf40f3cb48dd89d994ca285ced18fd775872d0cb","tid":2036913,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866543deaf14d898994c3f950ca3854f79d7124c","tid":2036913,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未到最壞 香港人唔會搏"},{"pid":"b19137baf1b5aa0c3b53d421bc2a2063087d966d","tid":2036913,"uid":115988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:18:01.000Z","msg":"【527金鐘？】每次盲目複製成功抗爭經驗，都慘敗收場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2036949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2036949</a>"},{"pid":"79af019725083268e6fae8209cea5d9a71b2dfed","tid":2036913,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pPfCpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pPfCpj.jpg&h=802027f7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}